      <odd id="aspace_cc9e98b2627f15ba80635b90e8c6cae9">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 13-M-2 (YRG 13-M-2), Records of the master of Ezra Stiles College.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_297c507b6be3e6d73713ac145106603b">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were transferred from Ezra Stiles College, 1979.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_b9403b3a5470eff0f300eb2bebd9d53d">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>Access to the records is partially restricted. See Collection Contents for details.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
